---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { ArrowDown, GithubLogo, ExternalLink } from "radix-svelte-icons"
---

<Layout title="Letsmoe">
	<div class="section h-[100vh] top-[80px] absolute bg-base-100 text-center">
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 items-center justify-between fixed left-[50%] h-[calc(100vh-80px)] translate-x-[-50%] py-16 w-full px-4">
			<img src="/images/kyrgizstan.webp" class="rounded-full my-0 w-2/3 max-w-[482px]" alt="Me">
			<a href="" class="no-underline "><h1 class="neon !text-8xl my-0">Moritz Utcke</h1></a>
			<ArrowDown size={48} class="animate-bounce"></ArrowDown>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="section absolute top-[100vh] bg-base-200 w-full h-auto min-h-[100vh] px-4">
		<div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto py-16">
			<h1>Projects</h1>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
				<div class="card w-full bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
					<div class="card-body">
						<div class="flex flex-row gap-4">
							<img src="/icons/meta.svg" width="64" class="!my-0">
							<h2 class="card-title !my-0">META</h2>
						</div>
						<p>META is a compiler writing toolchain optimized for speed and reliability. It is easy to pick up and extremely flexible.</p>
						<div class="card-actions justify-end gap-4">
							<a href="https://github.com/the-meta-lang" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg"><GithubLogo size={32}></GithubLogo> View on GitHub</a>
							<a href="https://meta-lang.com" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg"><ExternalLink size={32}></ExternalLink> Website</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card w-full bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
					<div class="card-body">
						<div class="flex flex-row gap-4">
							<img src="/icons/meta.svg" width="64" class="!my-0">
							<h2 class="card-title !my-0">Gyro</h2>
						</div>
						<p>A multi-language, statically typed, syntax extensible programming language built for speed and customizability.</p>
						<div class="card-actions justify-end gap-4">
							<a href="https://github.com/gyro-lang" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg"><GithubLogo size={32}></GithubLogo> View on GitHub</a>
							<a href="https://gyro-lang.com" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg"><ExternalLink size={32}></ExternalLink> Website</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto py-16">
			<h1>About Me</h1>
			<p>I'm a self-taught software engineer from Germany who loves traveling. I'm cycling around the world through over 60 countries at the moment.</p>
			<p>I occasionally dip my toes into stuff that i didn't know yet. I know a decent amount of programming languages both object-oriented and functional as well as a good amount of x86 Assembly (i don't know how that happened either) ðŸ˜†</p>
			<p>I've done a few projects, mostly web-focused or compilers/languages and have most definetely spent too much time in front of this rectangular screen...</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>

	.section {
		scroll-snap-align: start;
	}
	.neon {
		color: #fff;
		text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #919191, 1px 1px 1px #919191,
			1px 3px 1px #919191, 1px 4px 1px #919191, 1px 2px 1px #919191,
			1px 3px 1px #919191, 1px 7px 1px #919191, 1px 4px 1px #919191,
			1px 4px 1px #919191, 1px 10px 1px #919191, 0 0 3px #fff,
			1px 9px 3px rgba(16, 16, 16, 0.4),
			1px 11px 5px rgba(16, 16, 16, 0.2),
			1px 12px 17px rgba(16, 16, 16, 0.2),
			1px 15px 30px rgba(16, 16, 16, 0.4);
		opacity: 0.75;
	}

	.neon:hover {
		animation: glitch .375s infinite;
	}


@keyframes glitch {
  0% {
    text-shadow: 0.05em 0 0 #00fffc, -0.03em -0.04em 0 #fc00ff,
      0.025em 0.04em 0 #fffc00;
  }
  15% {
    text-shadow: 0.05em 0 0 #00fffc, -0.03em -0.04em 0 #fc00ff,
      0.025em 0.04em 0 #fffc00;
  }
  16% {
    text-shadow: -0.05em -0.025em 0 #00fffc, 0.025em 0.035em 0 #fc00ff,
      -0.05em -0.05em 0 #fffc00;
  }
  49% {
    text-shadow: -0.05em -0.025em 0 #00fffc, 0.025em 0.035em 0 #fc00ff,
      -0.05em -0.05em 0 #fffc00;
  }
  50% {
    text-shadow: 0.05em 0.035em 0 #00fffc, 0.03em 0 0 #fc00ff,
      0 -0.04em 0 #fffc00;
  }
  99% {
    text-shadow: 0.05em 0.035em 0 #00fffc, 0.03em 0 0 #fc00ff,
      0 -0.04em 0 #fffc00;
  }
  100% {
    text-shadow: -0.05em 0 0 #00fffc, -0.025em -0.04em 0 #fc00ff,
      -0.04em -0.025em 0 #fffc00;
  }
}

</style>
